{"tid":463381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港隊友賽巴林　球迷再噓國歌　高喊「We Are Hong Kong」","createTime":"2017-11-09T12:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T16:27:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":158,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c985f2999fb468e025bb41a9d4f7b33546b4d1","tid":463381,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/FLAG_ogme1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FFLAG_ogme1_1200x0.png&h=1c94f743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港足球代表隊今晚在旺角大球場友賽巴林。有球迷再次在奏唱中國國歌時，發出噓聲。另有球迷高叫「We Are Hong Kong」的口號與展示「Fight for Hong Kong」標語。有球場保安呼籲拍攝人士「唔好影啦」。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，幾個看台均傳出噓聲，有球迷用區旗蓋頭，背向球場舉中指。同時，大批記者在場拍攝，並在國歌環節後離開看台範圍，引起部分球迷不滿，指罵：「你哋嚟影波定影人？」<br />\n<br />\n開賽前夕，球迷進場前排隊通過安全檢查。球場門口的足總工作人員亦檢查入場者的隨身物品。同時就現場所見，警方派出不少便衣警員，於場外戒備。<br />\n<br />\n上週，全國人大常委會通過將《國歌法》納入香港《基本法》附件三，政務司長張建宗曾表示，港府將展開本地立法程序，但未言會否諮詢公眾。市民及非建制議員關注國歌法立法細節，擔心在大型活動如球賽、賽馬會否有市民誤墮法網、觸犯國歌法。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港隊上月10日在主場香港大球場以 2-0 擊敗馬來西亞的亞洲盃外圍賽中，有球迷噓中國國歌。亞洲足協決定對香港足球總會發出警告，並指如有再犯，或會嚴懲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%8B%E8%B3%BD%E5%B7%B4%E6%9E%97-%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E5%86%8D%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E9%AB%98%E5%96%8A-we-are-hong-kong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%258F%258B%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%259E%2597-%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2599%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2596%258A-we-are-hong-kong%2F&d=u2V4FAe0VNi%2BBpfrTfl2yP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=04a73446\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%258F%258B%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%259E%2597-%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2599%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2596%258A-we-are-hong-kong%2F&h=9a33aee7\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%8B%E8%B3%BD%E5%B7%B4%E6%9E%97-%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E5%86%8D%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E9%AB%98%E5%96%8A-we-are-hong-kong/</a>"},{"pid":"c05763558ec34901f4275755069ff71ffe8ba16e","tid":463381,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6769af95c564b52252af9cf1ed025699acc419a5","tid":463381,"uid":36178,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong is NOT China"},{"pid":"173e65114cc5c39617b716e0beba387b573bc9c8","tid":463381,"uid":74908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e67b0e6c2a60642e791907a247c42d59ee71d2f","tid":463381,"uid":33307,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"現場所見，幾個看台均傳出噓聲，有球迷用區旗蓋頭，背向球場舉中指。"},{"pid":"0ae88273a38911d14bed393064d627e5069c712a","tid":463381,"uid":37528,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"球迷好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfuck chi-na"},{"pid":"b5b339996aa8ec9523af781c989121181c4a5c18","tid":463381,"uid":6728,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9100bf110734ad924c0f60fa98eb34ae97f0fb","tid":463381,"uid":45983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"2fe61ee472ad99